"{\"uid\": \"si.com-gail-devers-q-a-it-s-show-out-time-for-sha-carri-richardson-team-usa-at-paris-olympics-100-meters\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Gail Devers\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s story is too remarkable to fit into a single introductory paragraph.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 84, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Platt\", \"score\": 0.999999999699412, \"rank\": 2.996010281040975e-10, \"text\": \"Gail\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Platt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Platt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fastest version: elite Olympian comes down with unknown health condition, struggles at the 1988 Seoul Games, drops 79 pounds, nearly loses a foot; is diagnosed with Graves\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 disease, embarks on stunning comeback, competes in two more Olympics (five total), wins three gold medals; becomes the subject of a TV movie,Run For the Dream:The Gail Devers Story.\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 112, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999986812327, \"rank\": 1.3189803366899336e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sha\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Carri Richardson is favored to win the 100 meters Saturday.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The last American woman to win the 100 meters at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6571046525461234e-23, \"text\": \"American woman\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gail Devers, at the 1996 Atlanta Games.\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gail Devers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SI spoke with Devers about the 100-meter dash, Team USA and what she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s up to now, at 53.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993827538362446, \"rank\": 0.0006158917981115698, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(This interview has been edited for length and clarity.)\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gail Devers:Man, that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s like 28 years ago.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gail Devers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gail_Devers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was not my concern at all.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I volunteer as a coach at a local high school.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The kids are texting about all these things.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like,Gail,someone just broke your 24-year-old Olympic record[in the 100-meter hurdles].\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m like,I didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know I had it,so OK!\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the same thing with bringing back the gold.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think this year, more than any other, we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve sent a great team to Paris.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999998121851094, \"rank\": 1.878152234563218e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If this isthe year, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to be a joyous time.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:The U.S. team is one of the hardest teams to make.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The best example is the 100-meter hurdles final [at U.S. trials] alone.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our fourth- and fifth-place runners [Nia Ali and Tonea Marshall, respectively, who both ran season-best times] could make the Olympic final.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nia_Ali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nia Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nia_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nia_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re sitting at home.\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hard to pick.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s go back to trials and see who made the team.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First of all, they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re young.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s their first Olympic games.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That makes you hungry.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the three that made the team [Richardson, Melissa Jefferson and Twanisha Terry] are from the same camp.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.625788952686177e-14, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melissa Jefferson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lizzo\"}, {\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twanisha_Terry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Twanisha Terry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twanisha_Terry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twanisha_Terry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have the same coach [Dennis Mitchell].\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Mitchell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.943358800427441e-35, \"text\": \"Dennis Mitchell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Mitchell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Mitchell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s show-out time.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you watch Sha\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Carri, all of them, practice, they all show up.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s certainly capable.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s forget about those five rings.\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the same thing we do every day, on the track\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094execute what you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve been taught.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:Everything was different\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094translating, transportation, hotels, training.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what progress is.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2225, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You want each generation to get better and better.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, we have the Diamond League.\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999959950401, \"rank\": 3.0226392705745895e-09, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back then, we didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have meets in the states.\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So you had to go to Europe.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re all riding the bus together, riding on planes together, riding on the trains.\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:That was when I should have been on top of the world.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I was, for a moment, because I had broken the American record for the 100-meter hurdles, in college.\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2581, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.997622600811796, \"rank\": 0.0023667697316393822, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statisticians are saying,If she just runs what she ran a couple months,we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re gonna have a medal.\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I got to the Games and the bottom fell out.\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I ran slower than I ever ran.\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a problem.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took three years before I was ever diagnosed.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was constantly losing weight, tired all the time, couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t sleep.\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had problems with my eyes, bulging eye pain.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As an athlete, you know your body, and you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re like,Something\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not right.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, I got diagnosed.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Grave\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s disease is an auto-immune disease that causes hyper-thyroidism.\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two years later, I came back, and I won my first Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3255, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then the other shoe dropped.\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:I was still having problems, throughout that whole ordeal, with my eyes.\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Running over hurdles, everything was blurry.\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could never see the hurdles clearly.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had learned to negotiate going over those hurdles.\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What the rhythm is.\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s eight steps from the blocks to the first hurdle.\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s three steps in between.\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Five steps off the last hurdle to the finish line.\", \"from\": 3626, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to run in rhythm.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because if I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m running in rhythm, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m running like everybody else.\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to sprint and take those hurdles.\", \"from\": 3785, \"to\": 3825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought it was the residual effect of the Grave\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s.\", \"from\": 3826, \"to\": 3880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But three decades later, I was having problems.\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 3928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I stopped driving at night.\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 3956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The lights coming at me were blinding.\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After three decades, I found out my eye problems were from a separate-but-related condition called Thyroid Eye Disease.I call him TED, because if somebody\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been living with you for 30 years, he deserves a name.\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4095, \"end\": 4102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thyroid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thyroid\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thyroid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thyroid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to become that voice, hope, advocate for other people.\", \"from\": 4210, \"to\": 4270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:Take care of your body\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and I mean beyond getting ready for races.\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go to doctors.\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Find a TED specialist.\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4365, \"end\": 4368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_Education_Association\", \"score\": 0.9886971087664896, \"rank\": 0.011432106372625258, \"text\": \"TED\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_Education_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_Education_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Think long-term.\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Go and find a specialist and ask for a comprehensive exam.\", \"from\": 4398, \"to\": 4456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 Don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t take the marathon route with healthcare.\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you know better, do better.\", \"from\": 4510, \"to\": 4540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope my story gives people belief and hope.\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When [doctors considered amputating her foot], I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m like,OK,you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re going to take my foot.You\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re not going to take my joy.\", \"from\": 4587, \"to\": 4713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:My dad always said I was a force to be reckoned with.\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we have the Gale Force Foundation [also listed online as the Gail Devers Foundation, Inc.].\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4787, \"end\": 4797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gale_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gale Force\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gale_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gale_Force\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I look back at my life, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m a teacher.\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 4910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, the world is my classroom.\", \"from\": 4911, \"to\": 4942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GD:That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the plan.\", \"from\": 4944, \"to\": 4965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 4993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Greg Bishop is a senior writer for Sports Illustrated who has covered every kind of sport and every major event across six continents for more than two decades.\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5058, \"end\": 5069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Bishop\", \"score\": 0.9999950627965526, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Greg Bishop\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greg_Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 5093, \"end\": 5111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0029733554103754e-21, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He previously worked for The Seattle Times and The New York Times.\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5244, \"end\": 5261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Seattle_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Seattle Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Seattle_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Seattle_Times\"}, {\"begin\": 5266, \"end\": 5284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"score\": 0.999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.720539494812451e-11, \"text\": \"The New York Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is the co-author of two books: Jim Gray\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s memoir, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTalking to GOATs\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d; and Laurent Duvernay Tardif\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cRed Zone\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 5286, \"to\": 5412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bishop has written for Showtime Sports, Prime Video and DAZN, and has been nominated for eight sports Emmys, winning two, both for production.\", \"from\": 5413, \"to\": 5555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5413, \"end\": 5419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.999969237410155, \"rank\": 2.3829711224207293e-05, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 5436, \"end\": 5444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Showtime_Networks\", \"score\": 0.9999307350264193, \"rank\": 6.926977132940047e-05, \"text\": \"Showtime\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Showtime_Networks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Showtime_Networks\"}, {\"begin\": 5469, \"end\": 5473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7856654450648948e-13, \"text\": \"DAZN\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\"}, {\"begin\": 5508, \"end\": 5520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Emmy_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"sports Emmys\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Emmy_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Emmy_Awards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has completed more than a dozen documentary film projects, with a wide range of duties.\", \"from\": 5556, \"to\": 5646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bishop, who graduated from the Newhouse School at Syracuse University, is based in Seattle.\", \"from\": 5647, \"to\": 5738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5647, \"end\": 5653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.999969237410155, \"rank\": 2.3829711224207293e-05, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 5730, \"end\": 5737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\", \"score\": 0.9999999969677447, \"rank\": 2.9498639508639835e-09, \"text\": \"Seattle\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5817, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 5818, \"to\": 5840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 5917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 5918, \"to\": 6112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6045, \"end\": 6063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0029733554103754e-21, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 6113, \"to\": 6201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 6202, \"to\": 6334, \"entities\": []}]}"